Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.55,0:22:51.20,EDJP,,0,0,0,fx,{\an5\blur5\fad(300,300)\fscx100\fscy100\pos(960,1035)}巻き戻そう 抓んだ竜頭回し
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.34,0:22:55.29,EDJP,,0,0,0,fx,{\an5\blur5\fad(300,300)\fscx100\fscy100\pos(960,1035)}奇想夢譚になっていく
